text: Denise Yvonne Dowse (February 21, 1958 â€“ August 13, 2022) was an American actress. She is best known for her roles as Mrs. Yvonne Teasley in the Fox teen drama television series Beverly Hills, 90210, Judge Rebecca Damsen in the CBS drama series The Guardian, and Dr. Rhonda Pine in the HBO comedy-drama television series Insecure. On August 5, 2022, Dowse was hospitalized for meningitis and she later fell into a coma.
